      {
        "id": 3112892,
        "name": "Dan Kravitz",
        "username": "Dan_Kravitz",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/958977/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-02-28T00:26:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>No surprise here with good provenance.  I thought I had a bargain with a 30 year old Sonoma Cab at a buck a year.  You came in under forty cents a year!  I hope all of them are equally good.  I wouldn\u2019t push my luck and lay them down for too long .</p>\n<p>Dan Kravitz</p>",
